DotFiles ReadMe
Author: DakotaK
Email: dakota@ddev.im
Date: 06/19/2014 
------------------------------

Requirements:
  git-scm - Used to get the files from the repository.

Usage:
  1. Change to home directory (cd ~)
  2. Clone the files to the local machine (git clone git://github.com/dakotak/dotfiles.git)
  3. Make the setup script executible. (chmod +x ~/dotfiles/make.sh)
  4. Execute the setup script. (~/dotfiles/make.sh)

To Update local sources run "git pull origin master"
  - I am going to abstract this function out to the make.sh script.


Tested Operating Systems:
  - Ubuntu Server 12.04.4 LTS
